abstract: "Professional methodological paper providing a conceptual definition and industry positioning of LLM-first website architecture. The study clarifies AEO, GEO, LLMO, Entity Engineering and Knowledge Graph integration, and proposes design principles for web presences interpretable by human users, classical search engines and generative AI systems."
